Introduction
====

Cikada is a pdf presentation tool. 

It is licensed in GPLv3.

Installation
====

$ autoreconf -i
$ mkdir build ; cd build
$ ../configure
$ make
$ sudo make install

Usage
====

The simplest way:

$ cikada your-pdf-file

If you want to use fullscreen, you can

$ cikada -f your-pdf-file

If you do not want to save some memory, you can

$ cikada -s 9999 your-pdf-file

It can load all the pages once unless the page number of your pdf file is bigger than 9999.

